headline: A tidal wave of cash hits Georgias Senate race
author: Patricia Murphy
sentences: In this episode of the Politically Georgia podcast, AJC political insiders Greg Bluestein and Patricia Murphy breakdown how the Democrat will use the $25 million hes amassed -- and how GOP frontrunner Herschel Walker plans to respond.
Three months into this election year and U.S. Sen. Raphael Warnock has already broken another fundraising record.
